      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一张Pezkuwi中继链的架构图。核心是把Pezkuwi Node和Pezkuwi Runtime放在同一个子图里，体现它们属于The Pezkuwi Relay Chain这个整体。",
