    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "FRAME是底层框架，它和Pezkuwi Runtime之间是虚线连接，表示一种依赖或调用关系。Pezkuwi SDK Node Libraries则是通过虚线连到Pezkuwi Node，说明SDK库是外部调用节点的接口。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FRAME",
        "PezkuwiRuntime",
        "PezkuwiSDK",
        "PezkuwiNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我来画一下：左边放FRAME，右边是Pezkuwi子图，子图内部上下排列Pezkuwi Node和Pezkuwi Runtime，最右边放Pezkuwi SDK Node Libraries。FRAME虚线连Runtime，SDK虚线连Node。",
      "elements_involved": [
